659
00:32:49,196 --> 00:32:51,782
It... It's under the couch.

660
00:33:02,538 --> 00:33:04,042
Cool. Let's go.

661
00:33:04,326 --> 00:33:06,442
Uh, I don't think it's cool, actually.

662
00:33:06,967 --> 00:33:10,833
I saw him sniffing around
Mercer's casino sports book

663
