669
00:33:25,195 --> 00:33:27,272
You gave Sonoma state the playbook?

670
00:33:27,346 --> 00:33:28,911
Larry was in on it, too.

671
00:33:30,576 --> 00:33:31,540
No one will know it was you, Kurt.

672
00:33:31,586 --> 00:33:33,620
Just turn in your pages
tomorrow like everyone else.

673
00:33:33,677 --> 00:33:35,503
And just let the team
get their asses kicked?

674
00:33:35,556 --> 00:33:37,662
