What do you owe them?

675
00:33:39,445 --> 00:33:40,981
I guess you don't know me that well.

676
00:33:46,557 --> 00:33:49,061
I can't believe you got
so much done that fast.

677
00:33:49,317 --> 00:33:51,541
Well, only one of
those dents is serious.

678
00:33:51,685 --> 00:33:53,770
The windows and paint
will take another day or so.

679
00:33:54,327 --> 00:33:55,491
It's not so bad.

680
00:33:56,175 --> 00:33:57,851
So, hey, the dean's a pal of yours?

681
00:33:57,905 --> 00:33:59,461
You actually made friends
with somebody?

682
00:33:59,537 --> 00:34:00,930
